name: Shawna
description: Shawna is one of the best dancers there is. Rumor has it, she even beat Slamson in a dance-off. She hopes to join the 916 Crew next season to show off her skills.

name: Splash
description: Splash has been perfecting his shot since he was a young Kaiju. His skills are now unmatched as he holds the title of back-to-back Champion of the Kaiju 3-Point Contest.

name: George
description: Nobody warms the bench quite like George. Even from the sideline, George is an important asset to the team. He never stops cheering and does a great job of keeping the crowd hyped.

name: Sam
description: Honored as one of the best flopping actors in the game, Sam holds the record for winning the most calls in his favor. At his home, he proudly displays all his flopping trophies in his living room.

name: Marc
description: Marc is a professional air guitarist. He's been practicing for years and is sure to turn a few heads in the crowd when his favorite song comes on.

name: Bran
description: Bran is a young entrepreneur constantly looking for new business opportunities. He loves going to Kings games and making connections with other fans. You never know where one may lead.

name: Rite
description: Poems, short stories, novels - you name it. Rite writes them all with passion! Although a creative mind, he dedicates each of his books to spellcheck for saving him from what could have been some more than embarrassing moments.

name: Jimmy
description: Jimmy is a foodie. He loves trying new dishes and admittedly spends more money on food than anything else. His all-time favorite meal at Golden 1 Center is the chicken strips and fries from Porchetta House. Yum!

name: Tito
description: Tito has mastered the art of the Dad Joke. Depending on the day, his jokes will either make you laugh or cringe, but he still enjoys telling them.

name: Malaak
description: Malaak has been an engineer for over 20 years. Every time she attends a Kings game, she's reminded of how impressed she is with the unique design of Golden 1 Center.

name: Armen
description: Armen is impulsive and his friends love it. He frequently buys last minute tickets to Kings games through the Fast Break offer for him and his friends to enjoy fun nights out.

name: Ally
description: Ally used to be an introvert. Now she loves to be around people - especially at Kings home games where she is surrounded by thousands of fellow Kings fans.

name: May
description: May is athletic; playing multiple sports throughout her life. She secretly wants to join the dunking ushers at halftime to show off her hidden skills.

name: Cal
description: Cal loves all things Sacramento and Kings basketball. He and his sister, Luna, often compete over who is the bigger fan but they both agree that the Kings are the best team.

name: AJ
description: AJ just recently started watching basketball and he loves it! He is always looking for ways to learn more about the game. Luckily, his brother Johnny is a basketball expert and shares all the knowledge he picks up from the Kings.

name: Aurore
description: Aurore holds the record for most t-shirts caught from the t-shirt cannon at Kings games.

name: Joey
description: Joey recently volunteered to join the dunking ushers during the halftime show. Unfortunately, all his practicing didnâ€™t pay off and he missed every single dunk. At least the fans enjoyed the show!

name: Drew
description: Drew puts his friends game day outfits to shame with his great taste in fashion. He always has the newest and freshest gear from the Team Store in his wardrobe. Just be careful not to step on his shoes!

name: Pedro
description: HODL (aka Hold on for Dear Life) is Pedro's motto! It applies to his recent dabbling in cryptocurrency as well as his love for the Kings.

name: Trev
description: If there is one thing you can count on, it's that Trev will always makes the right move - on and off the court. His teammates love him and he's on track for a wildly successful career.

name: BP
description: BP's handles are unmatched, watch out for your ankles when playing against him. His main rival is a great defender named Zakyy who loves the challenge.

name: Zakyy
description: Zakyy is an intense defender who does not like any nonsense. His favorite defensive matchup is against a great dribbler named BP.

name: Kris
description: Being a psychic, Kris can predict the future.

name: Rue
description: Rue is notorious for the crazy pranks she pulls on her friends and family. She once got into a pranking war with Slamson but Slamson got the last laugh.

name: Ari
description: An aspiring magician, Ari loves magic tricks. Her favorite trick is making free tickets appear out of thin air!

name: Chrissy
description: Chrissy grew up loving the water after learning how to sail from her father. She enjoys spending time on her boat on the Sacramento River.

name: Kat
description: After a long career as a doctor, Kat now enjoys the retired life. She spends most of her day watching TV and keeping up with Kings basketball.

name: Milo
description: Milo is the loudest Kaiju on the court and always makes his presence be known. His teammates love him for his nonstop communication on defense, but they wish he would tone it down with the amount of messages in the team's group chat.

name: Yusuf
description: Yusuf spends most of his time playing video games with his friends or following Kings Guard Gaming. His favorite spot in Golden 1 Center is the Esports Studio.

name: Seem
description: Down by 2 with a few seconds on the clock? No need to worry - give Seem the ball and he will knock down the shot with no issue.

name: Storm
description: Storm has an unmatched energy and can play all 48 minutes in a game without problem. He is a defender's worst nightmare because he never stops running.

name: Adan
description: Adan gets his competitive spirit from a sibling rivalry with brother AJ. Their most recent competition was a pie eating contest where Adan was victorious.

name: Robbie
description: Luck is a great skill to have. Thankfully, Robbie's luck also rubbed off on you.

name: Gigi
description: It's very rare for Gigi to get stressed out. She has the ability to remain calm in even the most chaotic and stressful situations. The only time you'll catch her a little uneasy is during the final seconds of a close Kings game.

name: Erin
description: Erin loves art and enjoys wandering the streets of downtown looking for new murals. She hopes to one day create her own mural in the DOCO Plaza outside of Golden 1 Center.

name: Chad
description: To Chad, trash talking comes second nature. Over the years, he's had a lot of practice when facing off against his twin brother Brad.

name: King
description: One of King's favorite things to do is win. He is a great team-player for that reason since he values winning over individual stats.

name: Erik
description: Erik and his friends love to rock out. They have jam sessions in the car to get hyped for Kings games.

name: Cass
description: Cass is an experienced traveler, she has been to over 50 countries in the world. Her most recent trip was to Mumbai to watch the Kings play in the first ever NBA game played in India.

name: Monique
description: Monique is a big innovator and is constantly looking for ways to be involved with new technologies and ideas. She is a big fan of the industry leading blockchain projects the Kings have been involved in.

name: Colin
description: Colin is a true data analyst. He always has the Kings + Golden 1 Center app open during games so he can get a live feed of all the stats in realtime.

name: Dom
description: Many of his fellow Kaijus strongly admire Dom's drive to be a professional basketball player. Dom spends hours every day perfecting his craft with the goal of becoming a professional.

name: Vlad
description: Vlad is one of the most famous and talented Kaiju basketball players in the world. Many young players view him as their role model and learn to play by watching old videos of him on the court.

name: Ian
description: Ian is a big fan of social media and considers himself a first adopter. He loves checking out the Kings social media pages for the funny memes and innovative content.

name: Frankie
description: Frankie loves an audience. He is always performing in front of a crowd and has even learned to juggle, ride a unicycle, dance, and do magic.

name: Joseph L
description: One of the first heavy investors in Ethereum and a major influential figure in the blockchain world. Joseph has founded multiple successful companies and is currently working on a decentralized blockchain production studio called Consensys.

name: Cole
description: Cole is known for being an incredibly kind and friendly person. He gets along with everyone he meets (including Lakers fans). He is so nice that he is willing to give you a gift for being a Kings fan!

name: Levi
description: Levi is an incredibly talented magician. His favorite trick is pulling Kings tickets out of a hat.

name: Leila
description: Leila is a known winner and has many medals and trophies to prove it. Like Leila, you are also a winner!

name: James
description: James loves to dance. His favorite part of a Kings game is trying to get on the Dance Cam so he can show off his moves. He may not be the best dancer, but at least he has fun doing it.

name: Casey
description: Casey is one of the greatest 3 Point shooters among Kaiju. His greatest rival is Splash, a fellow Kaiju, who just beat him in dramatic fashion at the Kaiju 3-Point Contest. If only he could re-shoot that final shot at the buzzer.

name: Kev
description: Although Kev may be a bench warmer, he is always looking to help the team improve. He is eager to provide feedback to his teammates and was recently honored with the 6th Kaiju of the Year award.

name: Kurt
description: Kurt is a well-known flopper. His funny antics cause the crowd to erupt in laughter everytime he he attempts a flop. Let's hope he doesn't hurt himself next time.

name: DJ
description: DJ recently discovered his newfound skill for air drumming. Whether practicing in his car or at his desk, he hopes to get on the jumbotron and show off his talents.

name: Susan
description: Susan has been an entrepreneur for years. Her favorite time of year is in February when she competes in the Kings Capitalize Startup Contest against the region's other best startups.

name: Mags
description: Mags is a contributing author to thousands of articles all over the internet about the Kings. Known in the sports scene for her wealth of knowledge, her goal is to be a guest on the Deuce & Mo Podcast to share her passion with other fans.

name: Xan
description: Xan loves food - and documenting his meals. Unfortunately, his food often gets cold by the time he starts eating because he spends too much time perfecting the best shot. His social media is full of delicious meals spent with his friends and family at DOCO restaurants.

name: Tay
description: Tay loves making her friends and family laugh with his witty jokes. One day, she hopes to do a Stand Up Comedy Show at Golden 1 Center in front of thousands.

name: Andre
description: Andre studied Engineering at Sacramento State and just landed his dream job at Golden 1 Center. Supporting concerts and games, Andre lives for the thrill of the event.

name: Tess
description: Tess loves doing things on a whim. She'll spontaneously buy tickets to a Kings game, a concert, or even a foreign country. She is a great friend to have since she is always down for an adventure.

name: Clyde
description: Similar to his cousin Ally, Clyde is one of the most social Kaiju. You can often find him spending time in DOCO meeting new people and playing games on the lawn.

name: Air
description: Air is one of the most athletic Kaijus. He won the most recent Kaiju Dunk Contest receiving a perfect score of 50 on every single one of his dunks.

name: Luna
description: Luna loves all things Kings! You can find her at almost every home game using her Kings Pass and cheering in the crowd.  She often calls herself the biggest Kings fan but her brother Cal would disagree.

name: Johnny
description: Johnny is a very inquisitive Kaiju and loves to learn more about the NBA and the Kings. He loves looking at the players' advanced stats in the app and listening to the Deuce & Mo Podcast for recent news.

name: Conti
description: Conti is an avid autograph collector. He has over 30 signed Kings basketballs in his collection.

name: Shay
description: Shay is known among her friends for her bravery. She once volunteered to join the dunking ushers during the halftime show and got a standing ovation from the crowd. They even offered her a permanent spot on the team for her performance.

name: Jess
description: Jess loves to rock her Kings swag. She owns over 10 custom Kings jerseys but her favorite is the new Kings Classic Edition jersey celebrating 35 years of basketball in Sacramento.

name: Jakob
description: Jakob was introduced to blockchain technology by his good friend and fellow Kings fan Pedro. One of the first things Jakob learned about cryptocurrency is HODL (which means Hold on for Dear Life).

name: Caleb
description: Caleb is one of the best people to attend a Kings game with. He knows so much about basketball and is great at breaking down the plays to explain what is happening at every moment.

name: Blur
description: Blur is one of the best dribblers among all of the Kaijus. Many of his fellow players learn new moves by watching him. Blur loves to embarrass his competition by dribbling the ball through their legs.

name: Kai
description: Kai is the type of Kaiju who prefers to have a highlight block than dunk. When he plays, expect a lot of steals and blocks sure to get the crowd excited.

name: Caiti
description: Being a psychic, Caiti can predict the future.

name: Ry
description: Ry is popular among his classmates for his crazy antics. He's always been the class clown and loves making his friends and family fall off their chairs laughing.

name: Wiz
description: One of the most famous magicians in the Kaiju world is Wiz. His prodigy, Ari, has been training to learn his skills over the last few years. Wiz's favorite trick is making things appear out of thin air...like Kings tickets!

name: Jordy
description: Jordy considers himself a professional inner tube sailor. You can find him tubing down the American River on hot summer days in Sacramento.

name: Jack
description: It took a while for Jack to ease into retirement. All the free time was tough the first year, but now he's enjoying the time and follows the Kings more closely than ever.

name: Marcos
description: Marcos prides himself on his communication skills. He speaks over five languages and is looking to learn more. When planning a trip, he is a great person to bring along.

name: Alexi
description: Alexi enjoys playing any type of game - sports, video games, board games, you name it! While Alexi plays games to unwind and have fun, his sister Cecile is very competitive and always plays to win.

name: Sue
description: Sue has been her team's clutch player ever since her championship game in high school. Scoring 10 straight points, including the game winner at the buzzer, was just the start of her career.

name: Jay
description: Fellow Kaijus hate guarding Jay in pickup games. He never gets tired and can simply beat the competition by out running them. At least defending him is a good work out!

name: Cecile
description: Cecile enjoys competing in any type of game - sports, video games, board games, you name it! While Cecile plays games to win, her brother Alexi plays games to relax and have fun.

name: Miko
description: Luck is a lucky skill to have. Thankfully, Miko's luck also rubbed off on you!

name: Sven
description: Like most Kaijus, Sven loves to come home from a long day of work and just chill. His favorite way to relax is on the couch, watching a Kings games with a pizza and his best friends.

name: Ray
description: Ray fancies himself an art connoisseur. Of all the great art in Sacramento, his favorite piece is the Jeff Koons "Coloring Book" sculpture in DOCO.

name: Brad
description: Brad and trash talking are synonymous. Growing up a twin, Brad and his brother Chad engaged in some friendly banter through sports.

name: Prince
description: Prince is a known winner. Whether it is in board games, sports, or even contests, you can count on Prince to win.

name: Scotty
description: Scotty is an up and coming DJ. Although still learning the scene, he's got his sights set on playing a post-game concert after a Kings game. One of his favorite parts of Golden 1 Center is the professional music recording studio.

name: Ryan
description: Ryan considers himself an innovator. He loves supporting the Kings on the court, but admires the innovative projects they spearhead.

name: Lauren
description: Similar to her brother Colin, Lauren loves diving into the advanced analytics and statistics of basketball. She frequently uses the Kings + Golden 1 Center app during Kings games to stay up to date with all of the realtime stats.

name: Nikki
description: Like her twin brother Dom, Nikki is an incredibly ambitious Kaiju. She works hard every day to achieve her dream of being a professional basketball player.

name: Felipe
description: Felipe is one of the most influential Kaiju basketball players in the world. Not only is he a great professional on the court, but he also does a lot off the court in the community.

name: Iris
description: Iris has been a social media enthusiast for years. She loves checking out the Kings social media page to stay up to date with the latest Kings news, highlights, and hilarious memes.

name: Syd
description: Syd and her brother Frankie are multi-skilled performers who have been entertaining audiences for years. Syd dreams of being able to perform her signature unicycling act during halftime of a Kings game.

name: Ryan H
description: Ryan H is an incredible writer and entrepreneur. His work influences many individuals throughout the world with the  teachings of Stoicism, being from Sacramento, he is also a huge Kings fan and loves to support his city and team!

name: Vitalik
description: One of the most innovative individuals in the blockchain world who has also won multiple awards. Vitalik is the co-founder and inventor of Ethereum. He is also a talented writer who co-founded Bitcoin Magazine.

name: Layla
description: Layla loves magic and learning new tricks to show her friends and family. Her newest trick is making tickets appear out of thin air.

name: Hasan
description: A local of the Sacramento region, Hasan is a successful & multi-talented comedian, writer, producer, actor, and more! He has already won several awards and continues to grow in popularity. He is a huge Kings fan and loves to support his local team.

name: Pomp
description: Pomp is one of the most influential and intelligent individuals in the blockchain world. He is a Co-Founder and Partner at Morgan Creek Digital. He also writes a great newsletter called "Off The Chain" to help people better understand the crypto industry.
